---
// BoltSite 競合優位性セクション
---

<section id="competitive" class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      
      <!-- セクションタイトル -->
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          競合優位性
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          なぜBoltSiteが選ばれるのか？他社との違いを比較
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 技術比較表 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden mb-12">
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead class="bg-gray-100">
              <tr>
                <th class="text-left py-4 px-6 font-semibold text-gray-900">比較項目</th>
                <th class="text-center py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-blue-600">BoltSite<br><span class="text-xs text-gray-500">(Cor.inc)</span></th>
                <th class="text-center py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-gray-700">大手制作会社</th>
                <th class="text-center py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-gray-700">フリーランス</th>
                <th class="text-center py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-gray-700">WordPress</th>
                <th class="text-center py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-gray-700">Wix</th>
                <th class="text-center py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-gray-700">Jimdo</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200">
              <tr>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-gray-900">初期費用</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">
                  <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">0円</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">100万円〜</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">50万円〜</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">30万円〜</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">5万円〜</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">3万円〜</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-gray-900">月額料金</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">
                  <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">15,000円〜</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">10万円〜</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">5万円〜</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">2万円〜</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">1万円〜</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">8,000円〜</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-gray-900">表示速度</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">
                  <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">0.3秒</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">1-3秒</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">1-5秒</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">3-10秒</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">2-8秒</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">2-6秒</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-gray-900">セキュリティ</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">
                  <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">最高レベル</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">高</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">中</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">低</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">中</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">中</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-gray-900">カスタマイズ性</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">
                  <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">完全対応</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-600 font-semibold">完全対応</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">制限あり</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-600 font-semibold">完全対応</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">制限大</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">制限大</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-gray-900">サポート</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">
                  <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">24時間対応</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">営業時間内</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">個人依存</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">コミュニティ</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">営業時間内</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">営業時間内</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-gray-900">スケーラビリティ</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">
                  <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">無制限</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-green-600 font-semibold">高</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">中</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">中</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">低</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">低</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="bg-gray-50">
                <td class="py-4 px-6 font-medium text-gray-900">保守コスト</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center">
                  <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">月額のみ</span>
                </td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">高額</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">変動</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-red-600 font-semibold">高額</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">中</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 text-center text-yellow-600 font-semibold">中</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- 採用技術 -->
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-12">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">採用技術</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Astro.js</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">静的サイト生成で最高のパフォーマンス</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Firebase Hosting</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Googleのインフラで安定した配信</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Cloudflare CDN</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">世界最大級のCDNで高速配信</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">実績例</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-blue-500">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">cor-jp.com</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">多言語対応でグローバル展開</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">0.3秒表示</span>
                <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">4言語対応</span>
                <span class="bg-purple-100 text-purple-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">SEO満点</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border-l-4 border-green-500">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">nogyodata.com</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-3">Firebase CMSで効率的なブログ運営</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">高速表示</span>
                <span class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">CMS連携</span>
                <span class="bg-orange-100 text-orange-800 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">保守性向上</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- なぜ速いのか？ -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 text-center">なぜ速いのか？</h3>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <!-- WordPress vs BoltSite -->
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">WordPress vs BoltSite</h4>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-red-50 rounded-lg">
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">WordPress</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-red-600 font-semibold">3-10秒</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">BoltSite</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-green-600 font-semibold">0.3秒</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
              <p><strong>WordPress:</strong> データベース読み込み、PHP処理、プラグイン実行</p>
              <p><strong>BoltSite:</strong> 静的ファイル配信、CDN最適化、Jamstack</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- 技術スタック比較 -->
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">技術スタック比較</h4>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-red-500 rounded-full"></div>
                <div class="text-sm">
                  <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">WordPress:</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-600"> PHP + MySQL + サーバー処理</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></div>
                <div class="text-sm">
                  <span class="font-medium text-gray-900">BoltSite:</span>
                  <span class="text-gray-600"> Astro.js + Firebase + CDN</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-blue-800">
                <strong>結果:</strong> BoltSiteはWordPressの<strong>10倍以上高速</strong>で表示されます
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
